          :Else ⍝ general
              (vals vecs code)←Dgeev mat
          :EndIf
     
      :Else ⍝ complex
          :If Sym mat ⍝ hermitian
              (vals vecs code)←Zheev mat
     
          :Else ⍝ general
              (vals vecs code)←Zgeev mat
          :EndIf
     
      :EndIf
      ⎕SIGNAL code/11
      vv←vals Join vecs
