    Fourier←{⍺←1 ⋄ ⍵ RunFn 'idft' 'dft'⊃⍨1+0⌈⍺}
    ∇ data←data RunFn func;rank;shape;count ⍝ n-D Discrete Fourier Transformation
      (rank count)←(⍴,×/)shape←⍴data
      :If 1<count ⍝ non-scalar
